{"tid":1432702,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［推介｝澳洲歌手Troye Sivan 你可能想屌嘅男人","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T05:35:53.000Z","uid":300241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4caf846b4837547dd4e47c8925f2a47617bfb945","tid":1432702,"uid":300241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:51:13.000Z","msg":"其實佢係外國都已經好紅，不過香港好似冇乜人識咁，所以就推介下佢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VoSN0f8S5-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVoSN0f8S5-M&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO71m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=1e8db038\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VoSN0f8S5-M</a><br />\n<br />\n由於之前佢嘅blue neighbourhood三部曲已經俾人介紹過<br />\n<br />\n所以今次想推介幾首上年推出嘅專輯Bloom入邊幾首歌俾大家。<br />\n<br />\n第一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />My My My!<br />\n<br />\n這首歌的內容主要係叫對方唔好否認同埋逃避呢段感情<br />\n<br />\n同佢一齊「做愛做嘅事」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k5TqNsr6YuQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk5TqNsr6YuQ&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO71m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=a5c75ce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k5TqNsr6YuQ</a><br />\n<br />\n第二首 plum <br />\n<br />\n呢一首講到關於一段愛情進入冷卻期嘅不安，即使係再靚再甜蜜嘅嘢都會有變質嘅一日...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CMWzsk__jcw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCMWzsk__jcw&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO71m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=17fd111d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CMWzsk__jcw</a><br />\n<br />\n第三首 What A Heavenly Way To Die<br />\n<br />\n上一首歌Plum入面佢感嘆熱戀期嘅結束，但呢度他好似搵到永恆嘅真愛，<br />\n<br />\n佢相信會同愛人過一個美好人生，沒有遺憾咁死去，<br />\n<br />\n因爲而家嘅佢可以在愛人身旁安然離去，所以會係個幸福嘅死亡（A Heavenly Way To Die)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ncoOwXNVpDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FncoOwXNVpDc&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO71m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=9ae5c6fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ncoOwXNVpDc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S樓豬唔係基佬"},{"pid":"72aa4ea2595a74a0da7344d7bcecb8300f4623c1","tid":1432702,"uid":300241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XKbXtf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XKbXtf.png&h=0c9eb35d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}